== In mythopoeia ==
{{See also|Category:Fictional creation stories}}
In [[mythopoeia]] an artificial mythology is created by the writer of [[prose fiction|prose]] or other fiction. The authors in this genre integrate traditional [[mytheme|mythological themes]] and [[archetypes]] into fiction. Some also feature creation myths:
* [[Ainulindalë]] from [[Tolkien]]'s ''[[The Silmarillion]]''

